Challenge 2: Join Subjects into Single String
Display subjects in UI
Input :
subjects = ("Math", "Science", "English")

# Traditional loop
subjects = ("Math", "Science", "English")
sub = ""
for i,s in enumerate(subjects, start=1):
    sub = f"{i}.{s} "  # Space add chesthe chudaniki baguntundi -- with f-string
  # sub += s + " " ----  with +
    print(sub)
Output:
1.Math 2.Science 3.English 
