Challenge 3: Reverse Each Student Name
Data masking requirement
Input
students = ("Anu", "Ravi")

# without loop
students = ("Anu","Ravi")
reverse_name = list(map(lambda s: s[::-1],students))
rev_str_name = ", ".join(reverse_name)
print(reverse_name)
print(rev_str_name)

Output:
['unA', 'ivaR']
unA, ivaR
